269
00:16:50.492 --> 00:16:54.192
So these slides provide a high level overview of

270
00:16:54.292 --> 00:16:57.532
MIDD as a tool to support drug development.

271
00:16:58.352 --> 00:17:02.212
As a quantitative approach, MIDD covers a wide range

