00:17:31.712 --> 00:17:32.312
details.

282
00:17:33.192 --> 00:17:34.152
Broadly speaking,

283
00:17:35.092 --> 00:17:38.892
MIDD involves the development and application of

284
00:17:38.952 --> 00:17:42.632
exposure based biological and pharmacological

285
00:17:42.892 --> 00:17:46.782
models derived from preclinical and clinical

286
00:17:46.852 --> 00:17:50.212
data sources to improve the efficiency of drug

287
00:17:50.252 --> 00:17:53.791
development, patient care, and regulatory decision.

288
00:17:56.692 --> 00:17:59.852
So MIDD provide a framework

289
00:18:00.372 --> 00:18:03.852
combining mechanistic understanding with quantitative

290
00:18:03.992 --> 00:18:07.616
reasoning to support the extrapolationIt

291
00:18:07.776 --> 00:18:11.756
enable us to leverage existing data and knowledge

