00:18:21.396 --> 00:18:25.356
Also design more informative trials and select the right

296
00:18:25.476 --> 00:18:27.796
dosage in the pediatric population.

297
00:18:30.716 --> 00:18:33.936
Regarding trial design, for example, a strong

298
00:18:33.996 --> 00:18:37.596
